{"tid":286068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港男菲律賓賭場做大耳窿 遭兇徒槍殺爆頭亡","createTime":"2017-06-16T10:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T10:13:55.000Z","uid":46420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fac9d31927f598edd2f6b666d63dc934d9f2ca5c","tid":286068,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"香港男子在菲律賓遭槍殺身亡。據當地傳媒報道，死者為一名60歲香港男子，譯音為張永森，據說是一名賭場大耳窿，居於馬尼拉。警方正調查案件是否與其業務有關。<br />\n<br />\n事發於周三(14日)晚上當地時間約9時半，事主在菲律賓馬尼拉的帕拉那克市(Paranaque City)機場路一酒店附近，正等候的士往會合女友，其間突然遭一名身份不明、戴頭套的槍手走近，向其頭部開槍，兇徒行兇後跳上接應的電單車逃去無蹤，事主在送院途中已證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n現場遺下大灘血迹，警方在事發現場撿獲一枚子彈殼。事後死者女友得悉噩耗大感震驚，並向警員透露，男友曾借貸予賭場客人，早前曾與人發生紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170616&amp;guid=56837229&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170616%26guid%3D56837229%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=raAy0EHAou65JN6gQfc7rVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=d17ddb4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170616%26guid%3D56837229%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=701a375b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170616&amp;guid=56837229&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n抵死啦,去D無口齒嘅國家放數,死咗都唔抵可憐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7972789a69d825a0374c830dcfd31b7c49a5dc9b","tid":286068,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"大耳窿俾人殺係抵死嫁"}]}